ecome applicable to more diverse types of stars, thanks to new spectrometers\non very large telescopes, and since ongoing photometric searches are expected\nto discover additional bright host stars of transiting exoplanets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 12 Jul 2016 20:00:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-12-07"}
